+------------------------------------------------------------+
|                    Frontend (Angular)                     |
|  +------------------------------------------------------   |
|  |  Web Server (Nginx or Apache)                           |
|  |  - Deployed on AWS EC2, Google Cloud, or any server    |
|  |  - Serves Angular application                           |
|  |  - Hosts static files (HTML, CSS, JS)                   |
|  +------------------------------------------------------   |
+------------------------------------------------------------+

                    | (HTTP Request)

+------------------------------------------------------------+
|                    Backend (API)                          |
|  +------------------------------------------------------   |
|  |  Node.js / Express or ASP.NET Core                     |
|  |  - Deployed on AWS EC2 or Azure App Service            |   |
|  |  - Communicates with frontend via REST API             |
|  |  - Logs requests and responses to a monitoring system  |
|  +------------------------------------------------------   |
+------------------------------------------------------------+

                    | (Database Operations)

+------------------------------------------------------------+
|                    Database (SQL/NoSQL)                   |
|  +------------------------------------------------------   |
|  |  Database Server (AbsanteeDB)          |
|  |  - MySQL                          |
|  |  - Deployed in cloud (e.g., AWS, Azure, or Google Cloud)|
|  |  - Manages PatientAccount Data                          |
|  |  - Provides failover, backups, and replication         |
|  +------------------------------------------------------   |
+------------------------------------------------------------+
